<h1>Articles</h1>
<h2>Our blog has <%= count_unarchived_articles %> active articles and counting!</h2>
<%= link_to "Create a new article!", new_article_path %>
<h3>Blog current public articles:</h3>
<%= render 'articles/articles_list', articles: @articles, filter: VisibleFeature::PUBLIC %>

<h3>Blog archived articles:</h3>
<%= render 'articles/articles_list', articles: @articles, filter: VisibleFeature::ARCHIVED %>



